  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n76/mode/1up">73</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n77/mode/1up">74</ref>.</p>
      <p>ceyappaṭuporuṇ mūṉṟaṉaiyum paṟṟi varum vāypāṭukaḷai virikkiṉṟār.</p>
<p>i - ḷ. kāppu mutalākac citaippīṟākac collappaṭṭa irupatteṭṭupporuḷum avaipōlvaṉa piṟavumākiya ammutaṟporuṇmēl varum ellāccollum iraṇṭām vēṟṟumaippālaveṉṟu colluvar pulavar. e - ṟu. eṉṟāveṉpatu eṇṇiṭaiccol.</p>
<p>iṉṉellām puṇariyaṉilaiyiṭaip poruṇilaikkutavātu eṇṇiṉkaṇ vantaṉa. muṉṉar varuvaṉavaṟṟiṟkum ītokkum.</p>
<p>ammutaleṉṟatu kūṟappaṭṭa ceyappaṭuporuḷeṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>u-m. eyilaiyiḻaittāṉ eṉpatu iyaṟṟappaṭuvatu. kiḷiyai yōppum; poruḷai yiḻakkum; nāṇai yaṟukkum; marattaik kuṟaikkum; nellait tokukkum; vēliyaip pirikkum; aṟattai yākkum; nāṭṭaic citaikkum eṉpaṉa vēṟupaṭukkappaṭuvaṉa. kuṟaittal curukkutalum ciṟitiḻakkac citaittalumām. aṟuttal ciṟitiḻavāmaṟ ciṉaiyaiyāyiṉum mutalaiyāyiṉum irukūṟu ceytal. ūraik kākkum; tantaiyai yokkum; tērai yūrum; kuricilaip pukaḻum; nāṭṭaip paḻikkum; putalvaraip peṟum; maṉaiviyaik kātalikkum; pakaivarai vekuḷum; ceṟṟāraic ceṟum; naṭṭārai yuvakkum; nūlaik kaṟkum; poṉṉai niṟukkum; ariciyai yaḷakkum; aṭaikkāyai yeṇṇum; ūraic cārum; neṟiyaic cellum; cūtiṉaik kaṉṟum; kaṇaiyai nōkkum; kaḷvarai yañcum eṉpaṉa eytappaṭuvaṉa. vekuḷaluñ ceṟalum kolaipporuḷavāyavaḻi vēṟupaṭukkappaṭuvaṉavām. ceṟal vekuḷiyatu kāriyam.</p>
<p>iyaṟṟappaṭuvatu orutaṉmaittākaliṉ, ataṟkoru vāypāṭē kūṟiṉār. ēṉaiya palavilakkaṇattavākaliṟ palavāypāṭṭāṉ virittuk kūṟiṉār.</p>
<p>aṉṉapiṟavumeṉṟataṉāl, pakaivaraip paṇittāṉ; cōṟṟai yaṭṭāṉ; kuḻaiyai yuṭaiyāṉ; poruḷaiyilaṉ eṉṉun toṭakkattaṉa koḷka.</p>
<p>kāppu mutalāyiṉa poruḷpaṟṟi yōtappaṭṭamaiyāṉ, ūraip purakkum; ūrai yaḷikkum; tantaiyai nikarkkum; tantaiyai yoṭṭum; tēraic celuttum; tēraik kaṭāvum eṉpaṉapōlvaṉavellāṅkoḷka.</p>
<p>iyaṟṟappaṭutal mutalākiya vēṟupāṭu kuṟippuviṉaic ceyappaṭu poruṭkaṇ ēṟpaṉa koḷka.	(11)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
